===Install ClioPatria and Amalgame===

  cd /opt
  git clone git://www.swi-prolog.org/home/pl/git/ClioPatria.git
  ./configure

  ./run.pl
    ?- cpack_install('amalgame').

Invoke http://localhost:3020 and set password for 'admin'.

